"     Patient information: Diabetic ketoacidosis (The Basics)",
"    </div>",
"    <span class=\"view\">",
"     View in",
"     <a class=\"lang\" href=\"./es-419/diabetic-ketoacidosis-the-basics?source=topic_page\">",
